citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:15 PM on
09-MAY-17.
* Inspector knocked on front door to the house of the licensee. Licensee stated that she had a prior scheduled
commitment and was just leave residence.
* Copy of inspection report was sent by regular mail.
